uild up to test-compile, so it recompiled the\nwhole reactor a second time inside unit-test (~1m35s) for a check that has\nnothing to do with unit tests.\n\nMove it into its own 'dependency-analysis' job that runs in parallel on its own\nrunner, off the critical path. The dependency check still runs on every PR and\npush with the same fail-on-warning behaviour (configured in dhis-2/pom.xml), and\nthe unit-test job no longer pays for the extra recompile.\n\nThe new job is added to the Slack-on-failure notification's needs so a failure\non master is still reported.","author":{"name":"Stian Sandvold","email":"stian@dhis2.org"},"id":"8e37dc079f65741de62688cdad50be86bd091445","tree_id":"88ad69dfeb2eb65166b3e94274f6ae7b8c0fad3b","timestamp":"2026-05-31T06:44:19Z","committer":{"name":"Stian Sandvold","email":"stian@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/5591308","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/repos","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/subscriptions"},"name":"dhis2-core","full_name":"dhis2/dhis2-core","description":"DHIS 2 Core. Written in Java. Contains th